replies.body:
Go to http://gameinfo.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/game-info/items/ and filter by items available on Summoner Rift.  When you get that working, filter by Mana Regen so you can check the stats on {{item:1056}} 

League's website is *garbage* when it comes to maintaining items. ***There is no official way, provided by Riot games, to check what items do, other than to queue up and AFK looking at the store.***

I love item sets. They don't generally need love, but when they do I *need* to fix them. Outsourcing the problem isn't an answer.
